## Verification
- `src/solana/rpc/transport.zig` defines the pluggable transport interface (`Transport`, `postJson`, owned deinit hook).
- `src/solana/rpc/http_transport.zig` implements the default HTTP transport using `std.http.Client`.
- `src/solana/rpc/client.zig` supports mock injection via `RpcClient.initWithTransport(...)`, with injected transport coverage in tests.
- JSON-RPC 2.0 envelopes are used in RPC request payloads and response handling (`jsonrpc`, `id`, `result` / `error`).

